&trans    &kp LG(LC(LEFT))  &trans         &kp LG(LC(RIGHT))  &trans                    &kp KP_MULTIPLY  &kp NUMBER_7  &kp NUMBER_8  &kp NUMBER_9     &kp KP_PLUS
